🙋🏻‍♂️ We are looking for a Senior Java FX Developer who enjoys solving challenging requirements in a scalable fashion both within a team setting as well as on an individual basis.
🔵Your skills in finding the right solutions in the project and solving complex tasks will become an auxiliary tool for the team.

You will work with a desktop application for online training of customers. Modernization/introduction of new functions - the main purpose of the application - is to automatically create Virtual Machines - testing/training environments for customers. More information would be provided during a general conversation with the Java developer.

Skills & Experience:
✔️Java FX;
✔️Advanced analytical, problem-solving and troubleshooting skills;
✔️Experience with agile delivery processes (Scrum, Kanban etc);
📌Intermediate spoken and written English and higher.

Requirements:

At least 4+ years of commercial development;
Strong Java/Kotlin;
C/C++ coding skills;
Experience in Android AOSP, HAL, Sensor HAL, AIDL, NDK, Sensor Manager;
Base knowledge of Linux kernel and device tree;
Script language knowledge (Python, bash);
Ability to quickly learn new technologies;
Ability to learn using technical documentation without assistance.
Responsibilities:

Develop android application for testing hardware and system services;
Review code and design;
Support software QA;
Help identify issues in custom system services.
О компании CHI Software
CHI Software is a software development company with 16 years of experience in the field. We collaborate with enterprises across the globe by delivering cutting-edge technology solutions for startups and medium-sized businesses. With over 600 engineers, we focus on Artificial Intelligence, Big Data, Cloud Computing, IoT, and Web solutions for Finance, Insurance, Real Estate, Retail, Media & Entertainment, and Travel industries. CHI Software is a global software development provider headquartered in Limassol, Republic of Cyprus, with distributed offices in Philadelphia (PA), USA, Kobe, Japan, and Lviv, Ukraine.

Our development team includes the following departments: web design, JavaScript, .NET, PHP, Ruby, Python, Java, C++, Mobile (Android and iOS), DevOps and QA, and we also have a great team of BI, BA, and Project Managers.

We constantly keep up with the current technology trends, developing Big Data, IoT, Machine Learning, Computer Vision, AR/VR, and Cloud (AWS, Azure) solutions.
